name: GodSaveKyivDAO
description:
God Save Kyiv. God Save Every Inch of Ukraine.

We want Peace, Not War!

This is a war on the people of Ukraine.

70% of the ETH raised will go fund refugees who have to flee from their homes.

20% will be used to sustain the project.

10% will be used for donations to share our cause and story.
payDisclosure: We are going to help refugees!
